GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_GovernanceSafetyTrust> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_GovernanceSafetyTrust> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#GovernanceSafetyTrust> ;
    narr:childCount "23"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "2aa450810c44b40b5dd3b24d9f36f965a99fceec" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of governance, safety, and trust within agentic systems, moving from early ethical questions of [consent and extraction](narr:Position_ConsentEthicsAdvisorRecording) toward technical enforcement of [agentic boundaries](narr:Narrative_AgentBoundsAndEscalation). The core tension remains the balance between organizational transparency and data sovereignty. While early discussions focused on [payment as a resolution to extraction](narr:Position_PaymentResolvesEthicsQuestion), recent work has shifted toward [per-task scoped permissions](narr:Narrative_PerTaskScopedPermissions) and [hard vs. soft segmentation](narr:Narrative_HardVsSoftSegmentation) to manage proprietary client data. Safety is framed through [anti-hallucination via citation](narr:Narrative_AntiHallucinationViaCitation), though this introduces the risk that a [stale graph with citations](narr:Position_StaleGraphCitationsWorse) is more dangerous than generic AI. To mitigate this, the project emphasizes [user-owned repositories](narr:Obs_UserOwnedRepo) and [non-negotiable provenance](narr:Narrative_HubMemoryProvenanceNonNegotiable) in hub summarization. Agent conduct is further constrained by [appropriateness gates](narr:Principle_AppropriatenessGate) and [disclosure-by-default](narr:Principle_DisclosureDefault), ensuring that agents maintain a clear [regulatory boundary](narr:Position_ProposalRegulatorySafeguard) while operating within the [Vouch identity infrastructure](narr:Narrative_VouchIdentityForAgents).""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgentBoundsAndEscalation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiHallucinationViaCitation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HardVsSoftSegmentation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HubMemoryProvenanceNonNegotiable> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerTaskScopedPermissions> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_VouchIdentityForAgents> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_AntiHallucination> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantAgentBoundaryQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantOAuthScopeQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletAgentBoundsQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletVouchPermissionsQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_StaleGraphDanger> ;
